overview: Vibes takes you to the pinnacle of adult entertainment, where the most elite beauties strut their stuff. Featured cover girls Emily Willis, Little Caprice, and Apolonia Lapiedra have never met, but sparks will fly when summer tourist season finds these sexy ladies staying in the same hotel. Rounding out this sensuous collection are scenes featuring Gizelle Blanco, Kali Roses, and Sky Pierce.
title: Vibes 4
